name: RaGeBMC
body:
#RaGeBMC 

RaGeBMC is a automated configuration voor Raspbmc.
This configuration will allow you to add torrent files to transmission web interface.
It will also download this rss feed from [ShowRSS](http://showrss.info/).
Here you can make you're own account and add the feed url to .flexget/settings.json
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
